---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base title="About - Eric">
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="page-container-narrow">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-semibold text-ink">About</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-muted">
        I build operating workflows that keep teams responsive without blowing
        up day-to-day execution. My work sits at the intersection of operations,
        revenue, and engineering, and I like being close to the details.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-4 text-muted">
        Outside of work, I have been with my fianc√©e for over five years, we
        have a two-year-old son, two dogs, a cat, and a ferret. I spend my time
        making and playing music, running, and being with my family.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-8 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
        <div class="surface p-6">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-ink">How I work</h2>
          <ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-2 pl-5 text-muted">
            <li>Start with business signals and decision points</li>
            <li>Design workflows that can be operated, not just launched</li>
            <li>Ship in increments with clear milestones</li>
            <li>Stay accountable through rollout and adoption</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="surface p-6">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-ink">What I value</h2>
          <ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-2 pl-5 text-muted">
            <li>Clarity over complexity</li>
            <li>Execution over theater</li>
            <li>Durable systems over quick fixes</li>
            <li>Ownership over handoffs</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="surface-muted mt-8 p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-ink">Operating focus</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-muted">
          I do best in environments where scale, accountability, and speed all
          matter. I work across leadership and delivery teams and keep the
          execution honest.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
